  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#Wireframe a Web App Idea\r\n\r\n**With your partner**, choose one of the following ideas for your website. Then, **each of you** will create 2 unique pages (4 in total):\r\n\r\n**Local Food Vendor Website**\r\n\r\n:::details [What should I include?]\r\n- **2 different pages**, e.g. Home, Menu, Order, or About Us\r\n- **Wireframe assets** such as images, placeholders, and structure (ignore styling and colors for now)\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n**School Club Website**\r\n\r\n:::details [What should I include?]\r\n- **2 different pages**, e.g. Home, Sign Up, About, Calendar\r\n- **Wireframe assets** such as images, placeholders, and structure (ignore styling and colors for now)\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n**Choose your own idea!**\r\n\r\n:::details [What should I include?]\r\n- **2 different pages**, e.g. Home, Menu, Contact, About Me\r\n- **Wireframe assets** such as images, placeholders, and structure (ignore styling and colors for now)\r\n:::",
